         <abstract><p>The hymns listed by Chaîne as items 172 and 220 seem to be identical, apart from a slight variance, the repetition of the word
            <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡</foreign> in the first verse. Another variant is witnessed by <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet18"/>, <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet24"/>, 
            <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet56"/> and <ref type="mss" corresp="EMIP00028"/>, which instead of the
            repeated <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡</foreign> have <foreign xml:lang="gez">ካልእ፡</foreign> in the first verse. </p></abstract>
